data.description: Welcome to this fantastic Chicago building! It's divided into two parts: one with five bedrooms and two bathrooms and the other with four bedrooms and one bathroom. Both kitchens have modern countertops. The whole place was redone in 2015, including a new roof and windows. It has a two-car garage and a big backyard. It's close to downtown and public transportation. With a few fixes, this place could be perfect for you. Schedule a visit soon!
